-coro-de-tolz.html";s:11:"author_name";s:7:"Euterpe";s:10:"author_uri";s:51:"http://www.blogger.com/profile/04825931404137087699";s:12:"author_email";s:19:"noreply@blogger.com";}i:17;a:12:{s:2:"id";s:70:"tag:blogger.com,1999:blog-3039319453248848087.post-4480190410208322996";s:9:"published";s:29:"2014-05-12T15:26:00.001+02:00";s:7:"updated";s:29:"2017-10-22T12:21:48.195+02:00";s:5:"title";s:35:"Tres coros de niños cantando juntos";s:12:"atom_content";s:985:"<DIV><FONT size=2 face=Arial>Aquí unas muestras de los de Tölz, los de Viena y  los de Augsburgo en perfecta unión musical:</FONT></DIV>  <DIV><FONT size=2 face=Arial><iframe width="420" height="236" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/F995fzEHOrM" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen></iframe></FONT></DIV>  <DIV><FONT size=2 face=Arial><iframe width="420" height="236" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/CxkCx12BN9A" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen></iframe></FONT></DIV>  <DIV><FONT size=2 face=Arial>Y aquí más vídeos del festival:</FONT></DIV>  <DIV><FONT size=2 face=Arial><A  href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Mt9tXAS4Uxk">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Mt9tXAS4Uxk</A></FONT></DIV>  <DIV><FONT size=2 face=Arial><A  href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=LB22abca9TE">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=LB22abca9TE</A></FONT></DIV>  <DIV><FONT size=2 face=Arial></FONT>&nbsp;</DIV>  <DIV><FONT size=2 face=Arial>Nuestro coro se encuentra ahora en Rusia: ¡mucha suerte!</FONT></DIV>";s:12:"link_replies";s:179:"http://toelzerknabenchor.blogspot.com/feeds/4480190410208322996/comments/defaulthttp://toelzerknabenchor.blogspot.com/2014/05/tres-coros-de-ninos-cantando-juntos.html#comment-form";s:9:"link_edit";s:82:"http://www.blogger.com/feeds/3039319453248848087/posts/default/4480190410208322996";s:9:"link_self";s:82:"http://www.blogger.com/feeds/3039319453248848087/posts/default/4480190410208322996";s:4:"link";s:86:"http://toelzerknabenchor.blogspot.com/2014/05/tres-coros-de-ninos-cantando-juntos.html";s:11:"author_name";s:7:"Eu